        {"@type":"Question","name":"Can I open a UK bank account without visiting the UK?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. 100% of the providers we recommend (Wise, Revolut, Mercury, Payoneer) offer a fully digital, remote onboarding process for non-residents."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"Which bank is best for Amazon FBA?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Wise and Payoneer are the best. They integrate perfectly with Amazon Seller Central and allow you to receive payouts in local currencies without high conversion fees."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"Do I need a UK phone number for 2FA?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"While not strictly required, having a UK virtual number is highly recommended for professional appearance and to ensure you can receive SMS codes reliably."}},
