        {"@type":"Question","name":"What is an ACSP and why do I need one for banking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"An Authorized Corporate Service Provider is a firm registered with Companies House to verify identities. Banks trust ACSP-verified founders significantly more, leading to higher approval rates."}}
