        {"@type":"Question","name":"Can I get a UK visa by opening a company?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Opening a company is the first step, but it does not automatically grant a visa. To move to the UK, you would typically look at the Innovator Founder Visa or Skilled Worker Visa."}},
