        {"@type":"Question","name":"Is a UK Ltd the same as an LLC?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. The UK does not have an LLC structure. A UK Ltd is the closest equivalent, providing limited liability but with separate-entity taxation rather than pass-through taxation."}},
